  <h2>Prerequisites</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>AWS account with appropriate permissions</li>
    <li>AWS CLI configured: <code>aws configure</code></li>
    <li>Terraform ≥ 1.5</li>
    <li><code>kubectl</code>, <code>helm</code>, and <code>eksctl</code></li>
  </ul>

